{"tid":1849233,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇新興加密貨幣 Pi corn","createTime":"2020-01-29T02:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T13:30:28.000Z","uid":247534,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"32831d88e489a708feb97e3c172d9877e70c46fe","tid":1849233,"uid":247534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:49:02.000Z","msg":"佢地團隊希望將Pi corn成為最具包容性的p2p市場，簡單又易用。<br />\n<br />\nPi使用的一致性算法：<br />\n基於StellarConsensusProtocol(SCP)和一個名為Federated Byzantine Agreement(FBA)的算法。這種算法沒有能源浪費，但是它們需要交換許多網絡消息，以便節點對下一個塊應該是什麼達成&quot;共識&quot;。每個節點可以獨立地確定一個事務是否有效。<br />\n重點：可以用手機挖礦。<br />\nApp store同google play 已經可以下載 有興趣可以search Pi network。<br />\n但目前處於佢地團隊講第二階段。估計上市要幾個月。但值唔值錢就唔知。<br />\n反正手機就挖到，樓主一於試下"},{"pid":"bd91ae22bf34cbc6411a6db04a4bb1a2a20ac285","tid":1849233,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:50:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />訓身</span>"},{"pid":"12ebdeae3afe26e6e41cdac124519d596ee22fc5","tid":1849233,"uid":3325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:59:03.000Z","msg":"無得交易點吹都係垃圾"},{"pid":"424bbd7d02404175e13d9c5da93f6030ecef1673","tid":1849233,"uid":247534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12ebdeae3afe26e6e41cdac124519d596ee22fc5","tid":1849233,"uid":3325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:59:03.000Z","msg":"無得交易點吹都係垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:05:47.000Z","msg":"bitcorn當年都冇得交易啦"},{"pid":"b024db33e00fe776caf99382a0512ea79e0966ab","tid":1849233,"uid":3325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"424bbd7d02404175e13d9c5da93f6030ecef1673","tid":1849233,"uid":247534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12ebdeae3afe26e6e41cdac124519d596ee22fc5","tid":1849233,"uid":3325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:59:03.000Z","msg":"無得交易點吹都係垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T0